Improving Neural Network Performance

1. Vanishing Gradients
    - Activation Functions
    - Weight Initialization 

2. Overfitting
    - Reduce Complexity/Increase Data
    - Dropout Layers
    - Regularization (L1 & L2)
    - Early Stopping

3. Normalization
    - Normalizing Inputs  -- Normalize the input features in same range (eg: Salary numbers are very high so need normalization basically scaling)
    - Batch Normalization
    - Normalizing Activations

4. Gradients Checking and Clipping

5 Optimizers
    - Momentum
    - Adagrad
    - RMSprop
    - Adam

6. Learning Rate Scheduler

7. Hyper-parameter Tuning
    - No. of hidden Layers
    - Neurons per layer or Nodes per layer
    - Batch Size
